div.p: My name is Andy (andyrak). I live in Shoreline, Washington and work as a Software Engineering Manager. I've been in software for 13 years as a full-stack engineer on multiple systems at multiple companies. I work on random projects for my homelab and interested in other OSS projects.

I'm looking to get more involved in OSS projects and your contributions will help me offset the personal time I spend coding! By offset, of course I mean ☕ or 🍺 to help fuel those long coding sessions.
